snippet.title: Is Johnny Depp As Bad As They Make Him Out To Be?
snippet.description:
Hollywood  actor Johnny Depp is in a lot of controversy due to his divorce with American actress and model Amber Heard.






Johnny Depp  is a famous movie star of films such as "Edward Scissorhands", "Sweeney Todd: The Demon Barber of Fleet Street", "Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl" and "Sleepy Hollow". This video is a speculation on the recent events between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's divorce. Holly Willoughby and Phillip Schofield discuss in This Morning, whether Johnny Depp is the bad one out of this situation or if Amber Heard is the real perpetrator of the domestic problems these two have faced. We also have the opinion of an ex Sun journalist and his reaction. Is Johnny Depp Hollywood actor the bad one in all this? Come and watch this interview for more!
tags: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Divorce
